NCOP PLENARY (VIRTUAL) 1. Questions to the Deputy President, 4 November 2020 2. Consideration of the Select Committee on Finance report on the Revised Fiscal Framework CAPE TOWN - Deputy President David Mabuza will answer questions virtually in the National Council of Provinces on Wednesday afternoon. The questions are mainly focussed on service delivery but, the issue of the municipal debt owed to Eskom is also on the agenda. READ: Mabuza: Corruption can't reign supreme The deputy president will also respond to questions on revitalising township and rural economies.